{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol\/set(readyTime:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/sourceprotocol\/set(readytime:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a source to be dispatched when the given monotonic time is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reached (or passed).","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","text":"gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the monotonic time is in the past (as it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"always will be if "},{"code":"readyTime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"text":") then the source will be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"dispatched immediately.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" then the source is never woken up on the basis","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of the passage of time."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispatching the source does not reset the ready time.  You should do"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so yourself, from the source dispatch function."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that if you have a pair of sources where the ready time of one","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"suggests that it will be delivered first but the priority for the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"other suggests that it would be delivered first, and the ready time"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for both sources is reached during the same main context iteration,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then the order of dispatch is undefined.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is a no-op to call this function on a [struct"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true},{"text":"] which has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"already been destroyed with [method"},{"code":"GLib.Source.destroy","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This API is only intended to be used by implementations of [struct"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Do not call this API on a [struct","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] that you did not create.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gint64","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"extendedModule":"GLib","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:4GLib14SourceProtocolPAAE3s